title: The Psychedelic Bus Of Dead Knowledge
description:
The Psychedelic Bus Of Dead Knowledge is 
" A trippy deadhead knowledge game loaded with psychedelic eye candy"

It's a CD-ROM trivia game with shitty low resolution Grateful Dead videos and music! It runs on Quicktime! Yay! Quicktime 4 is included. It's made for a 4:3 display and sqwishes in to 16:9. Yay!

If you can cope with the buggy shitiness of the whole ordeal, this shitty trivia game could possibly give you all you ever wanted out of life
